<h2> Testing and Verification of VLSI Systems (CS5227) </h2>
<h3> Indian Institute of Technology Tirupati, India</h3>

<hr>

<p> The course on Testing and Verification of VLSI Systems is generally a master level course which offers
to enable the students to be industry or research ready. <br> <br>
 
Detailed objective of the course could be found here:<a href="./desc.html"> cs5227 content. </a> <br>
